                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "Body",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Built from 304 stainless steel and architectural glass — no BPA plastics, painted finishes, or adhesive seals anywhere the water touches. Every unit is NSF/ANSI 42 &amp; 53 certified and individually pressure-tested before it leaves the workshop.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
