    "cert_deepdive_pdp": {
      "type": "section",
      "blocks": {
        "text_eyebrow": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Certified To What, Exactly</p>",
            "width": "100%",
            "max_width": "normal",
            "alignment": "center",
            "type_preset": "custom",
            "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
            "font_size": "0.75rem",
            "line_height": "normal",
            "letter_spacing": "loose",
            "case": "uppercase",
            "wrap": "pretty",
            "text_color": "#0f5e75",
            "background": false,
            "background_color": "#00000026",
            "corner_radius": 0,
            "padding-block-start": 0,
            "padding-block-end": 0,
            "padding-inline-start": 0,
            "padding-inline-end": 0
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "text_heading": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>Two Standards, Not Just One Badge.</h2>",
            "width": "100%",
            "max_width": "narrow",
            "alignment": "center",
            "type_preset": "h2",
            "font": "var(--font-heading--family)",
            "font_size": "1rem",
            "line_height": "normal",
            "letter_spacing": "tight",
            "case": "none",
            "wrap": "pretty",
            "text_color": "#202224",
            "background": false,
            "background_color": "#00000026",
            "corner_radius": 0,
            "padding-block-start": 10,
            "padding-block-end": 0,
            "padding-inline-start": 0,
            "padding-inline-end": 0
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "text_intro": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Most filters advertise \"NSF certified\" without saying which standard or what it actually tested. Here's the specific difference — and why it matters for what ends up in your glass.</p>",
            "width": "100%",
            "max_width": "narrow",
            "alignment": "center",
            "type_preset": "rte",
            "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
            "font_size": "1.0625rem",
            "line_height": "normal",
            "letter_spacing": "normal",
            "case": "none",
            "wrap": "pretty",
            "text_color": "#5c6368",
            "background": false,
            "background_color": "#00000026",
            "corner_radius": 0,
            "padding-block-start": 10,
            "padding-block-end": 0,
            "padding-inline-start": 0,
            "padding-inline-end": 0
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "custom_liquid_content": {
          "type": "custom-liquid",
          "settings": {
            "custom_liquid": "<div id=\"hs-cert-deepdive\" style=\"max-width:980px; margin:36px auto 0; padding-inline: clamp(4px, 2vw, 16px);\">\n  <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap:28px;\">\n    <style>\n      @media screen and (min-width: 800px) {\n        #hs-cert-deepdive > div { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }\n      }\n    </style>\n    <div style=\"border:1px solid #C8D1CC; padding:28px;\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; margin-bottom:16px;\">\n        <svg width=\"34\" height=\"34\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.4\"/><path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n        <div>\n          <span style=\"display:block; font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; font-size:0.6875rem; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#8B9398;\">Standard 01</span>\n          <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:1.25rem; color:#202224;\">NSF/ANSI 42</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.9375rem; line-height:1.65; color:#5C6368;\">Covers <strong>aesthetic effects</strong> — the things that affect how your water looks, tastes, and smells, not necessarily whether it's unsafe.</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px;\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:flex-start;\">\n          <span style=\"width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:#0F5E75; margin-top:8px; flex-shrink:0;\"></span>\n          <span style=\"font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.55; color:#202224;\">Chlorine taste and odor reduction</span>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:flex-start;\">\n          <span style=\"width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:#0F5E75; margin-top:8px; flex-shrink:0;\"></span>\n          <span style=\"font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.55; color:#202224;\">Particulate (sediment) reduction, Class I-VI ratings</span>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:flex-start;\">\n          <span style=\"width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:#0F5E75; margin-top:8px; flex-shrink:0;\"></span>\n          <span style=\"font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.55; color:#202224;\">Structural integrity and material safety of the unit itself</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"border:1px solid #C8D1CC; padding:28px;\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; margin-bottom:16px;\">\n        <svg width=\"34\" height=\"34\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;\"><path d=\"M12 3l7 3v6c0 4.5-3 7.5-7 9-4-1.5-7-4.5-7-9V6l7-3z\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/><path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n        <div>\n          <span style=\"display:block; font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; font-size:0.6875rem; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#8B9398;\">Standard 02</span>\n          <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:1.25rem; color:#202224;\">NSF/ANSI 53</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.9375rem; line-height:1.65; color:#5C6368;\">Covers <strong>health effects</strong> — contaminants that are regulated because of documented health risk, not just taste or appearance.</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px;\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:flex-start;\">\n          <span style=\"width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:#0F5E75; margin-top:8px; flex-shrink:0;\"></span>\n          <span style=\"font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.55; color:#202224;\">Lead and other heavy metal reduction</span>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:flex-start;\">\n          <span style=\"width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:#0F5E75; margin-top:8px; flex-shrink:0;\"></span>\n          <span style=\"font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.55; color:#202224;\">Cyst reduction (Cryptosporidium, Giardia)</span>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:flex-start;\">\n          <span style=\"width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:#0F5E75; margin-top:8px; flex-shrink:0;\"></span>\n          <span style=\"font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.55; color:#202224;\">VOC (volatile organic compound) reduction</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:24px auto 0; max-width:44rem; text-align:center; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.9375rem; line-height:1.65; color:#5C6368;\">Most filters advertise a certification without saying which one, or which specific contaminants it was tested against. HAUSTAS systems are tested to both standards — <a href=\"/pages/about-us\" style=\"color:#0F5E75;\">see the certificate</a> for the exact contaminant list and reduction claims.</p>\n</div>"
          },
          "blocks": {}
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_eyebrow",
