          "name": "Pre-checkout FAQ",
          "settings": {
            "custom_liquid": "<div id=\"hs-pdp-faq\" style=\"max-width:760px; margin:36px auto 0; padding-inline: clamp(4px, 2vw, 16px);\">\n  <details class=\"hs-pf-item\" open style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #C8D1CC; padding:6px 0;\">\n    <summary style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px; padding:16px 4px; cursor:pointer; list-style:none;\">\n      <svg width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;\"><path d=\"M12 4v16M6 8l6-4 6 4M6 16l6 4 6-4\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <span style=\"flex:1; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:1.0625rem; color:#202224;\">How do I know this is the right system for me?</span>\n      <span class=\"hs-pf-toggle\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; width:22px; height:22px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#0F5E75;\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M2 8h12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><path class=\"hs-pf-vert\" d=\"M8 2v12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/></svg>\n      </span>\n    </summary>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px 42px; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.9375rem; line-height:1.65; color:#5C6368; max-width:34rem;\">Use the comparison table above as a quick gut-check against a basic pitcher filter, and if you're weighing this against another HAUSTAS system, our team is happy to point you to the right one — <a href=\"/pages/contact\" style=\"color:#0F5E75;\">just ask</a> before you order.</p>\n  </details>\n  <details class=\"hs-pf-item\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #C8D1CC; padding:6px 0;\">\n    <summary style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px; padding:16px 4px; cursor:pointer; list-style:none;\">\n      <svg width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;\"><rect x=\"4\" y=\"9\" width=\"16\" height=\"11\" rx=\"1.5\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/><path d=\"M8 9V6a4 4 0 018 0v3\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/></svg>\n      <span style=\"flex:1; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:1.0625rem; color:#202224;\">Will it fit my sink or faucet?</span>\n      <span class=\"hs-pf-toggle\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; width:22px; height:22px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#0F5E75;\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M2 8h12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><path class=\"hs-pf-vert\" d=\"M8 2v12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/></svg>\n      </span>\n    </summary>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px 42px; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.9375rem; line-height:1.65; color:#5C6368; max-width:34rem;\">HAUSTAS systems are built to connect to standard residential fixtures without special adapters. If you have an unusual faucet or sink setup, message us before ordering and we'll confirm fit first — no guesswork.</p>\n  </details>\n  <details class=\"hs-pf-item\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #C8D1CC; padding:6px 0;\">\n    <summary style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px; padding:16px 4px; cursor:pointer; list-style:none;\">\n      <svg width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"7\" width=\"18\" height=\"13\" rx=\"1.5\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/><path d=\"M3 11h18\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/><path d=\"M7 4l0 3M17 4l0 3\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <span style=\"flex:1; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:1.0625rem; color:#202224;\">How fast does it ship, and what's in the box?</span>\n      <span class=\"hs-pf-toggle\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; width:22px; height:22px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#0F5E75;\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M2 8h12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><path class=\"hs-pf-vert\" d=\"M8 2v12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/></svg>\n      </span>\n    </summary>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px 42px; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.9375rem; line-height:1.65; color:#5C6368; max-width:34rem;\">Orders ship within 1–2 business days. Everything you need arrives in one box: your HAUSTAS system, the installed filter cartridge, all connection hardware, and a printed setup guide — nothing extra to source separately.</p>\n  </details>\n  <details class=\"hs-pf-item\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #C8D1CC; padding:6px 0;\">\n    <summary style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px; padding:16px 4px; cursor:pointer; list-style:none;\">\n      <svg width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/><path d=\"M8.5 12.5l2.5 2.5 4.5-5\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <span style=\"flex:1; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:1.0625rem; color:#202224;\">I installed it and something feels off — now what?</span>\n      <span class=\"hs-pf-toggle\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; width:22px; height:22px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#0F5E75;\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M2 8h12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><path class=\"hs-pf-vert\" d=\"M8 2v12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/></svg>\n      </span>\n    </summary>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px 42px; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.9375rem; line-height:1.65; color:#5C6368; max-width:34rem;\">You're still covered. The 100-night trial starts the day it arrives, not the day you decide — so you have plenty of time to actually live with it. If it's not right, return it any time within 100 nights for a full refund, no questions asked.</p>\n  </details>\n  <details class=\"hs-pf-item\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #C8D1CC; padding:6px 0;\">\n    <summary style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px; padding:16px 4px; cursor:pointer; list-style:none;\">\n      <svg width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;\"><path d=\"M12 3l2.5 5.5L20 9l-4 4 1 6-5-3-5 3 1-6-4-4 5.5-.5z\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.1\"/></svg>\n      <span style=\"flex:1; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:1.0625rem; color:#202224;\">Can I stock up on replacement cartridges now?</span>\n      <span class=\"hs-pf-toggle\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; width:22px; height:22px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#0F5E75;\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M2 8h12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><path class=\"hs-pf-vert\" d=\"M8 2v12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/></svg>\n      </span>\n    </summary>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px 42px; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.9375rem; line-height:1.65; color:#5C6368; max-width:34rem;\">Yes — each cartridge lasts about 6 months, and you can stock up on HAUSTAS Flow replacements and save 15% with code <strong>FLOWSAVE15</strong> at checkout, so you're never caught without one.</p>\n  </details>\n  <details class=\"hs-pf-item\" style=\"padding:6px 0;\">\n    <summary style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px; padding:16px 4px; cursor:pointer; list-style:none;\">\n      <svg width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;\"><path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/></svg>\n      <span style=\"flex:1; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:1.0625rem; color:#202224;\">Is the certification actually real?</span>\n      <span class=\"hs-pf-toggle\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; width:22px; height:22px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#0F5E75;\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M2 8h12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><path class=\"hs-pf-vert\" d=\"M8 2v12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/></svg>\n      </span>\n    </summary>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px 42px; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.9375rem; line-height:1.65; color:#5C6368; max-width:34rem;\">Yes — every unit is NSF/ANSI 42 &amp; 53 certified and individually pressure-tested before it leaves the workshop. <a href=\"/pages/about-us\" style=\"color:#0F5E75;\">See the certificate</a> for yourself.</p>\n  </details>\n</div>\n<div style=\"max-width:760px; margin:32px auto 0; padding-inline: clamp(4px, 2vw, 16px); display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:10px 28px; padding-top:24px; border-top:1px solid #C8D1CC;\">\n  <span style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; font-family: var(--font-accent--family); font-weight: var(--font-accent--weight); font-size:0.75rem; letter-spacing:0.06em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#202224;\">\n    <svg width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\" stroke=\"#3F7D5C\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\" stroke=\"#3F7D5C\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"/></svg>\n    100-Night Trial\n  </span>\n  <span style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; font-family: var(--font-accent--family); font-weight: var(--font-accent--weight); font-size:0.75rem; letter-spacing:0.06em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#202224;\">\n    <svg width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\" stroke=\"#3F7D5C\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\" stroke=\"#3F7D5C\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"/></svg>\n    15-Year Warranty\n  </span>\n  <span style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; font-family: var(--font-accent--family); font-weight: var(--font-accent--weight); font-size:0.75rem; letter-spacing:0.06em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#202224;\">\n    <svg width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\" stroke=\"#3F7D5C\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\" stroke=\"#3F7D5C\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"/></svg>\n    Free Shipping & Returns\n  </span>\n</div>\n<style>\n  #hs-pdp-faq details > summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }\n  #hs-pdp-faq details[open] .hs-pf-vert { display: none; }\n</style>"
